{"id": "1264180329401552988", "channel_id": "1262559584158089226", "type": 0, "author_id": "1223503015852380160", "author_name": "squire5771", "author_bot": false, "content": "基本和莉兹一样思路的一套超维潘，不同点在于先出艾瑞卡x再开鼠鼠钥令，因为需要叠力量之后尽可能多打鞭子输出", "timestamp": "2024-07-20T11:21:17.864000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1264180328562425917", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-20-18-46-59-540_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 245146, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262559584158089226/1264180328562425917/Screenshot_2024-07-20-18-46-59-540_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae2d&is=69ca5cad&hm=a471da8cfff418b7e578cd38e54b2d9d5b3837a212a9193dd20284175c230544&"}, {"id": "1264180329057488916", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-20-18-57-32-577_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 307859, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262559584158089226/1264180329057488916/Screenshot_2024-07-20-18-57-32-577_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae2d&is=69ca5cad&hm=0544eb7a60db6a44590f4b8586bc3972ccbf6631afdd6006db3342c844464a6e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1262559584158089226", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新版本超维奥尔拉配队分享帖", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1264292816079687710", "channel_id": "1262559584158089226", "type": 0, "author_id": "1223503015852380160", "author_name": "squire5771", "author_bot": false, "content": "超维盾击，思路是利用喜情绪的保留用钥令复制利刃（最好刻镜像或者跃迁），超维前一回合用艾瑞卡x叠盾（需要拿算力造物，这把没有导致卡手很难受），进空间切哀打三张防御叠盾，艾尔瓦和诺缔拉开大，再切怒奥尔拉开大，把利刃全部打出去。", "timestamp": "2024-07-20T18:48:16.778000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1264292815593275432", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-21-02-32-22-465_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 337996, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262559584158089226/1264292815593275432/Screenshot_2024-07-21-02-32-22-465_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc16f0&is=69cac570&hm=aba76121626b79560db2ee7deb258603e7a4f4362098d2f99504eccd1105f5c3&"}, {"id": "1264292815903522867", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-21-02-32-38-849_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 303606, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262559584158089226/1264292815903522867/Screenshot_2024-07-21-02-32-38-849_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc16f0&is=69cac570&hm=41b1ba7b21245fb03ed91510907b585273b920b1af0959ef2d76a05a0810b024&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1262559584158089226", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新版本超维奥尔拉配队分享帖", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174180524034637854"]}
